name: Xibalba Death
description: The second piece of the Xibalba series; Death. Some nebulae are the remnants of a dead star while others are acting as a nursery for the birth of a new star. Xibalba is the name of the dead star that represents the end and the beginning in Mayan mythology. Series consists of 3 pieces; Life, Death and Rebirth. Sound on.
